circ;ng ty lớn, c&ocirc;ng ty c&oacute; KH ở quốc tế, điểm cung cấp dịch vụ Internet.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Nhược điểm:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Chi ph&iacute; ho&agrave; mạng, gi&aacute; cước cao hơn nhiều so với g&oacute;i c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, hộ gia đ&igrave;nh.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Y&ecirc;u cầu phải c&oacute; GPKD.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18pt; color: #ff0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BẢNG GI&Aacute; WIFI C&Aacute;P QUANG D&Agrave;NH CHO DOANH NGHIỆP &amp;#8211; FPT QUẬN 12&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter wp-image-2636&quot; src=&quot;https://fptcapquang.info/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/ewrwer.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;1120&quot; height=&quot;405&quot; srcset=&quot;https://fptcapquang.info/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/ewrwer.png 929w, https://fptcapquang.info/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/ewrwer-300x109.png 300w, https://fptcapquang.info/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/ewrwer-768x278.png 768w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 1120px) 100vw, 1120px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://fptcapquang.info/internet-cap-quang-fpt-2018/#formtuvan&quot; class=&quot;button primary is-primary is-medium&quot;  &gt;     &lt;span&gt;ĐĂNG K&Yacute; TƯ VẤN NGAY&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;/a&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Thủ tục &lt;a href=&quot;https://fptcapquang.info/internet-cap-quang-fpt-2018/&quot;&gt;đăng k&yacute; Internet c&aacute;p quang FPT&lt;/a&gt; như thế n&agrave;o?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bước 1:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lựa chọn g&oacute;i cước C&aacute;p quang Wifi Quận 12- Ph&ugrave; hợp với nhu cầu sử dụng.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Trước ti&ecirc;n, qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng h&a